                     10ra-20va)&#xD; I-5) Tuesday (fols. 20va-31ra)&#xD; I-6) Wednesday (fols.
                     31ra-39rc)&#xD; I-7) Thursday (fols. 39rc-51ra)&#xD; I-8) Friday (fols.
                     52ra-81ra)&#xD; I-9) Saturday (fols. 81ra-93vc)&#xD; - Rāʾǝya Yoḥannǝs
                     “Revelation of John”(fols. 82vc-88vb)&#xD; - Tǝmhǝrta ḫǝbuʾāt “Teaching of
                     Mysteries” (fols. 92rc-93ra)&#xD; I-10) Homily by Cyriacus of Behnesa [Lāḥā
                     Māryām “Lamentation of Mary”] (fols. 94ra-98ra)&#xD; I-11) Maṣḥafa dorho “Book
                     of the Cock” (fols. 98ra-100v)&#xD; &#xD; Additiones 1-2.</summary>
